<br>
Leggings of Fiery Might (or other decent legs)- unless you're likely to be getting the rare plate legs off ele gods any time soon.<br>
<br>
Gloves of Crimson Sigil - rightclick extra 65dd proc to weapons never hurt anyone going for agro.<br>
<br>
Belt of Mastery - 125hp AOB belt<br>
<br>
Cloak of Manoeuvering - 115hp cloak with a dodge mod<br>
<br>
Cloudy Steel Mask - 125hp face, with the added benefit of rightclick invis if you don't have self invis clickie - clerics and paladins should prolly have first refusal on there though.<br>
<br>
Bracelet of the Shadow Hive - non interruptable 1 second shrink &gt; cobalt bracer or tinkered thingy, especially for a large race warrior with zero channelling.<br>
<br>
Ring of Resistance - reasonable hps, awesome resists.<br>
<br>
Look at other rings and earrings too<br>
<br>
For you specifically:<br>
<br>
1: Range slot could use a big boost<br>
2: Could easily upgrade bracers<br>
3: Get 41% haste (BP would work well for you)<br>
4: If you can move haste, a new cloak would be another big upgrade<br>
5: Earrings and belt would also benefit from a boost <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solinarinnoruuk>Solinar Innoruuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 346<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/10/03 7:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5225.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Question on Longevity of Items from Vex Thall.</span><hr size=1> Any non Raexs slot.  There is nothing with AC in PoP other than raexs, so fill up in VT.<br>
