<br>
Seriously, BP of Speed should be at (or near) the top of any warrior's list. In addition to moving haste to a slot you will not get better hps on with ANY existing drop, you also gain 30atk from the effect (=Venge 6), as well as the +dodge mod (hardest to find). I personally feel it's the best BP there is for a MT. Aten BP may have fancier stats, but I'd choose BPoSpeed every time.<br>
<br>
By 3rd best BP, I assume you're thinking Aten and Seru off the top of my head?<br>
<br>
BPoS: 125hps 60ac 30atk +Haste +5% dodge <br>
Seru BP: 125hps 75ac 15atk +30svP/F +15C/D/P +4regen<br>
Aten BP: 125hps 80ac 50atk +30svF/C<br>
<br>
I'd value the +dodge higher than those other stats, and moving haste to a slot you won't be upgrading for a very long time is an additional bonus.<br>
<br>
Further to that, is crippling your existing haste slot. Move haste and since you can wear FH cultural, there's +30hps on cloak right away with a FHCloak. There's loads of VT/post-VT cloaks out there, including ele planes. There's people in the ele planes now CURSING their GoDS or Bracers or Cloaks or wherever they have their haste, because it's crippling their upgrade path.<br>
